snippet.title: Ben 10 Power Trip! Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Will this be game over for Ben Tennyson?! 🎮
Co-op battle with frenemy Kevin 11, in Ben 10 Power Trip! Coming 9th October to PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch & PC. Pre-order now 👉 https://outrightgames.com/games/ben-10-power-trip/

#Ben10PowerTrip 🚋
